snippet.textDisplay: Coke Studio Bharat and they chose to open with this? Deeply disappointed 🥲 Where is the innovation, I wished you spent more attention to actual song than running ads and promoting your "Coke Studio Bharat". Seriously what's going on with all the Coke Studios. Coke Studio PK Season 14 was okay, yeah it was new. But then they copy it with Memu Agamu (which to me was total time killer), now this. The electronic beats and negligible live singing performance apart from casual moving aorund, im sick of it already. I only loved Coke Studio Bangla Season 1 last year. Music is dying folks, good music is dying 🤒
